replies.body:
The Q and R bug must be her trying to even the playing field and give other champs some chance (however small) to win against her.

but anyway, just try her in a custom game, and if she bugs out then send a ticket and if she doesn't throughout the custom, then that will give you confidence to play her in normals, and if it does bug out then apologise to your teammates and submit a ticket. 

if you are sure its going to happen, then film the game with whatever game recorder people use, so that when she does bug out, you have evidence to show riot, (and when you are videoing, ready to capture a bug, the bug never happens)
